Sothink SWF Decompiler v4.5

*********************
D e s c r i p t i o n
*********************

Sothink SWF Decompiler, a professional flash decompiler easily decompiles one or more SWF to FLA. It supports Flash 6, Flash MX 2004, Flash 8 and Flash CS3. This Flash decompiler can recover FLA and extract elements including shape, sounds, images, sprites, fonts, texts, ActionScript etc. It is compatible with ActionScript 3.0

SWF Decompiler Features

    * Convert SWF to FLA stably.
    * Export one or more SWF to FLV, SWF to element at one time.
    * Support exporting the resources to SWF or FLA format.
    * Extract element into various formats, including shapes, sounds, images, sprites, fonts, texts, ActionScript, etc.
    * Export the video file in FLV format from Flash movie.
    * Export ActionScript file in AS, HTML format.
    * Support Flash 6, Flash MX 2004 (7.0), Flash 8 and Flash CS3 (9.0).
    * Compatible with ActionScript 2 and ActionScript 3.
    * Support Flash components.
    * Provide a user-friendly interface (like Office 2007)

    * Invoke Flash SWF from User-friendly Explorer-like Windows.
    * Offer built-in player to play SWF on hard drive or network.
    * Supply the playback control bar to play, stop, forward, backward; zoom in/out Flash movie freely.
    * Navigate and browse resources in preview window before exporting.
    * View detailed properties of elements in Flash movies.
    * Optimizes the display of ActionScript in Resources Panel. When decompiling AS3.0, support showing AS Class structure like folder-tree according to its path in package.
    * Supports scanning the cache of IE and listing all Flash files you have viewed.
    * Supplies SWF Catcher for Firefox and SWF Catcher for IE.
